Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.12,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.54,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,W-What should we do?{NOTE:ど、どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.42,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Haven't we gone overboard?{NOTE:ちょっと酷すぎたんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.42,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori.{NOTE:ね、みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.30,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,We didn't have to go that far.{NOTE:こ、こんなにまでしなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Don't shift the responsibility to me alone.{NOTE:あたしだけを責める何て。良い事。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,All of us are in it together.{NOTE:これは皆でやってことなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It wasn't just me.{NOTE:あたしだけの悪いんじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.93,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Ah, captain…{NOTE:は、キャプテンが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We're not over yet.{NOTE:未だXXXないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll show you I can still accept another 50 serves.{NOTE:さ、あと五十球受けて見せるわ。}
