Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.07,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Hahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.49,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Captain, here.{NOTE:キャプテン、はい、これ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot about it.{NOTE:あら、忘れてた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.37,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,– I'll tie it for you.\N– Okay.{NOTE:あたし結んであげるわ。}
