Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.70,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's Kaimei Middle School. After we win with them, it's semifinals.{NOTE:明日は海明中学よ。これに勝てばいよいよ準決勝ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,The semifinals are not a problem.{NOTE:XXX二値予選なんか問題じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,The goal is to continue our spring streak and win the whole thing.{NOTE:春に続いて連続の全国優勝の目標よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Right, Kozue?{NOTE:ね、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And the arch nemesis is Fukuoka, all right.{NOTE:そしてその強敵はやっぱり福岡中学よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.75,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,We almost lost with them in the spring, didn't we?{NOTE:ねね、春の決勝戦の時は危なかったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.88,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. We have the best attacker in Japan after all.{NOTE:大丈夫。家には日本一のアタッカーがいるなんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.05,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Darn right.\N– Don't be careless.{NOTE:—XXXよ。\\N—油断はいかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.05,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Look at this.{NOTE:これを見たまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"Will they become first?\NFukuoka Middle School."{NOTE:日本一成るか福岡中。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"From defense to an attack team."{NOTE:守りから攻撃のチームね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"Megaton-class destructive power of Kakinouchi's attack."{NOTE:メガトン級の破壊力、垣之内選手のアタック。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Is it the same Kakinouchi-san?{NOTE:こ、これはXXの垣之内さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I got this newspaper from a friend of mine from the university times, who's now living in Fukuoka.{NOTE:その新聞は福岡にいる私の大学時代の友人に頼んで、XXんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.95,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,They're changing their model from defense to a powerful attack.{NOTE:福岡中学は守りから攻撃へとモデルチェンジをしている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.95,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,They'll be nothing like in spring.{NOTE:春のようにはいかないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:43.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Looks like they weren't just all talk in their challenge and have indeed become a wonderful team.{NOTE:やっぱりあたしに挑戦状よこしたXXって、素晴らしいチームに成っているのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:47.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I bet they're convinced they can win with us.{NOTE:あたしたちに勝自身が出来たんだわ。きっと。}
