Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Come on! Fight, fight!{NOTE:頑張って！ファイト！ファイト！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei is acting strange today.{NOTE:おかしいわ、今日のおケイ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.61,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,It hurts…{NOTE:苦しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei.{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Okei.{NOTE:どうしたの？おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.45,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Captain, I…{NOTE:キャプテン。あたし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.79,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I feel weird…{NOTE:どうXXか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What is it, Okei?{NOTE:どうしたの？おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.46,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I… I…{NOTE:目、目は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.38,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,I can't see!{NOTE:見えないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah! Okei!{NOTE:あ！おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei, come on.{NOTE:おケイ、ほら、しっかりして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Okei!{NOTE:大丈夫？おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Keep it together!{NOTE:ほら、しっかりしてよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.51,Alternative,Katori,0,0,0,,Okei!{NOTE:おケイ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.19,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Girls, listen!{NOTE:ちょっと、み、皆！大変よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What is it?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.98,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,O-Okei has collapsed!{NOTE:お、おケイは倒れたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.11,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.03,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,I wonder if she is all right?{NOTE:どうしたのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What happened?{NOTE:どうしたのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, Midori.{NOTE:あ、みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with Okei.{NOTE:おケイのXXちょっとおかしいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.91,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Okei, hang in there.{NOTE:おケイ、しっかりして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah, she has terrible fever.{NOTE:あら、大変の熱。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh? Whoa, you're right.{NOTE:え？あら、本当だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.88,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Hey, Kozue.{NOTE:ちょっと、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What the heck did you do to her?{NOTE:あなたは一体おケイになにをしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:48.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She just collapsed in the middle of our training.{NOTE:と、特訓の最球、吸入Xまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.26,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Tell us how it really was, captain.{NOTE:すごいのよ、キャプテンたら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.60,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,It was your training that has caused her to collapse.{NOTE:おケイは倒れてのに、無理に引き起こしてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It didn't cause it.{NOTE:あら、引き起こしただなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.10,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,It was terrible.{NOTE:酷かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.98,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,I've seen it myself.{NOTE:見てたずっとうしたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that.{NOTE:そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's harsh, Oyoshi.{NOTE:酷い、おヨシ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.82,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Save excuses for later. We need to take Okei to infirmary as soon as possible.{NOTE:言い訳は後にして。とにかく、おケイを早くに医務室X。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.86,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Naka, get going! Quickly!{NOTE:ナカ、頼むわよ。早く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.49,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.{NOTE:うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.32,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Okei, hang in there.{NOTE:おケイ、しっかりして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.82,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Be careful.{NOTE:あら、気をつけて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.91,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ozawa-san.\N– Hm?{NOTE:—小沢さん。\\N—うん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Get the janitor and bring the key to the infirmary.{NOTE:小使さんに話して、医務室の鍵を取ってきてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.87,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Hurry up!\N– Got that!{NOTE:—急いで！ —分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kakko, call Okei's house.{NOTE:カッコは直ぐおケイの家へ電話して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.33,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Got it?\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—いいわね？\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.29,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ofuku.\N– Eh?{NOTE:—おフク。\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:26.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Don't just stand here. Contact hospital.\N– Okay, then?{NOTE:—ぼさっとつ立ってないで。早く病院XXちょうだい。\\N—う、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:30.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Get a doctor to come here. Got it?\N– I'm on my way.{NOTE:—XXXお医者さんを。分かったのね？\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori.{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy{NOTE:富士見学園}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.03,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,I don't think it's anything serious.{NOTE:え。大したことはないと思いますけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.95,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Her temperature is a little high though so we thought it'd be better if we let you know.{NOTE:はい。ちょっと熱は高いXX知らせしといた方が良いと思いまして、それで…\\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.66,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the trouble.{NOTE:ま。どうもわざわざ有難うございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.66,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Please tell the doctor that I'll be there very soon.{NOTE:先生には直ぐXXXするとお伝えくださいまし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:11.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,Infirmary{NOTE:医務室}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.05,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,She suffers from extreme fatigue.{NOTE:軽い貧血ですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:21.98,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,I gave her sedatives so she sleeps well. It's better to let her sleep in here tonight.{NOTE:安定剤で眠らせていますが今夜は動かさないで、ここで寝かした方がいいでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.19,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the trouble.{NOTE:はい。どうもおせいはおかけました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.94,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Her heart has considerably weakened.{NOTE:心臓は大分弱っているですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:30.07,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,I advise you to have her heart thoroughly examined as soon as possible.{NOTE:何れ、精密検査を受ける必要がありますね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.70,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Do you think there is something wrong with her heart?{NOTE:あの、大分悪いでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:36.74,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,I can't say anything for sure until I see examination results.{NOTE:精密検査の結果を見なければ、未だ何とも言えませんが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.62,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's good that you let her do such a strenous exercise.{NOTE:過激な運動がいけなかったかもしれませんが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.58,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.12,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be on my way.{NOTE:じゃ、私はこれで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:47.84,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here so late at night.{NOTE:ま、夜分どうも有難うございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.55,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,What about you, girls?{NOTE:あ、君たちは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll all nurse her together tonight.{NOTE:はい。あたしたちは今夜皆で看病します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:57.47,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Ah, there's no need. You have your game tomorrow.{NOTE:あ、それはいけません。皆さんには明日の試合もあるんですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:01.77,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,I can take care of her by myself. Please go home.{NOTE:あの、この子あたくし一人で十分です。どうぞ、お帰りになって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:07.48,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,I agree. I called mister Hongou and let him know. There's no need to worry.{NOTE:それがいい。本郷先生には私の方から電話でよく話しておくから。心配はいらないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.40,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Well then.{NOTE:じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.32,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Thank you very much.\N– Thank you very much.{NOTE:—有難うございました。\\N—有難うございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll be on our way then, ma'am.{NOTE:では私達はこれで失礼させて頂きます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.41,Default,Kudou's mom,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, girls.{NOTE:ま、どうも有難うございました、皆さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Please take care of her.\N– Thank you.{NOTE:—どうぞ。お大事に。\\N—ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{NOTE:失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:36.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We promised to follow your coaching.{NOTE:あたしたちあなたのコーチに付いてX約束したわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,However, I think you went overboard this time.{NOTE:でも今度のことは明らかにあなたのやりすぎよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:45.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I had to hold a special training session with her.{NOTE:あたし特訓とは言っても、そんなに酷くは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:50.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Thanks to your training there's no knowing if\hOkei will ever be able to play volleyball again.{NOTE:でも、特訓が鯨飲でおケイはもうバレーを出来なく成るかもしれないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,You are our captain. It's okay if you're strict with us.{NOTE:それはキャプテンだから、厳しくするんな結構よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.91,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But there are boundaries.{NOTE:でも、それXX限度Xと思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.{NOTE:あたしは間違っていない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I did what was only natural as their coach.{NOTE:コーチとして当然のことをしたんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She must have been sick even before.{NOTE:そう。おケイは以前から病気だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It has to be it.{NOTE:きっとそうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.63,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd collapse from just that.{NOTE:でなきゃ、あのくらいの練習で倒れるはずはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.05,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,How about this, girls?{NOTE:さ。それじゃいいわね、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll make it clear in front of professor Hongou tomorrow.{NOTE:明日先生の前でこのXXをはっきりさせましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– I agree.\N– Agreed.{NOTE:賛成。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.31,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Let's go.\N– Yeah.{NOTE:—さ、皆行きましょう。\\N—行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Is that so?{NOTE:そうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry too much, though.{NOTE:ま、君たちはあまり心配しないように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.08,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It was an unfortunate accident.{NOTE:不良の事故なんだからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am deeply sorry.{NOTE:申し訳ありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's nothing you need to be sorry about.{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ。君が誤ることはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All what happens in the club is my responsibility.{NOTE:バレー部で起こったことは全て僕の責任なんだからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Professor.{NOTE:でも、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the case this time.{NOTE:この場合は違うと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:07.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,This accident was clearly caused by the extreme training.{NOTE:これは明らかに行き過ぎた至極が原因で起きた事故なんですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.52,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I think captain Ayuhara should assume responsibility for this.{NOTE:責任はキャプテンの相原さんがXべきだと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.56,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Exactly, exactly.{NOTE:そうよ。そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.57,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Of course, we know we need hard training.{NOTE:それは厳しすぎるのは結構ですけどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:19.11,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,But there are boundaries. Okei's case shows it well.{NOTE:でも、おケイのように成っちゃったら、元も子もないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why are you teaming up on me?{NOTE:あなた方は皆であたしのこと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:25.12,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,We were saying it was too strict from the start.{NOTE:あたしたちはね、前から厳しすぎるって言ってたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It was obvious that sooner or later it had to go down like this.{NOTE:誰かがこう成ることは分かってたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It just happened to be Okei.{NOTE:結局、おケイは緯線に成ったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori, how can you say that?{NOTE:みどり、何てこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:36.05,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She fainted during your training.{NOTE:でも、気絶する前、練習させたいじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We just want to avoid repeating this in the future.{NOTE:あたしたちは第二のおケイに成りたくないって言ってるのよ、皆で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:43.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okei was sick even before.{NOTE:おケイはね、前から病気だったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,– Really?\N– Say what?{NOTE:—本当？\\N—XXなのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.43,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,That makes it even worse.{NOTE:酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.06,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,You know about it and yet—{NOTE:病気だと分かってた、あんなこと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't know about it.{NOTE:知るはずないじゃないのあたしが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But it has to be the case.{NOTE:でも、きっとそうじゃないXXってるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.52,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's despicable.{NOTE:卑怯よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:58.86,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, you're covering your mistakes with a\hmade-up sickness and you call yourself a captain?{NOTE:こずえ。自分のXXXを人の病気せいにするなって、キャプテンとして最低だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Fine, what should I do then?{NOTE:あたしにどうしろうって言うんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:03.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Forfeit my captain title?{NOTE:キャプテンをやめろうって言いたいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Eh? Of course not…{NOTE:え？まさか。そこまでは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori. Be honest with me.{NOTE:みどり。はっきりったらどうなのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:13.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You just want to get rid of me, don't you?{NOTE:キャプテンを止めてしまえって？どうなのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.79,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Calm down, Ayuhara.{NOTE:ま、ま。そう興奮するんな、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:21.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But that's too much. I don't want to be a\hcaptain, whose whole team rebels against.{NOTE:だって、あんまりです。あたしだってXXXまで、キャプテンを続けたくないんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:27.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori, I misjudged you.{NOTE:みどり。あたしあなたを見損なったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:33.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I am only expressing opinion of everyone.{NOTE:あ、あたしはただ皆の意見を代表して言ってるだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Then all is the same.{NOTE:それから、皆もそうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:40.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't think you're qualified to play volleyball if you think like that.{NOTE:丸であたしを憎んそのように思っているらしいけどそんなことだったらあんたたちなんかもうバレーをやる資格ないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What would happen to the club if I quit?{NOTE:いっそXバレー部だって止めたらどうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:なんですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– As if.\N– Wow.{NOTE:まさか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.16,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,That was way out of line. I can't follow Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:XXXだわ。あたしは鮎原さんに付いていけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.75,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Me too.{NOTE:あたしもよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.75,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Us too.{NOTE:あたしも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Why don't you forfeit the captain title for now?{NOTE:どうだ？一度君はキャプテンを降りてみたらどうかと思うんだが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor?{NOTE:先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.61,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I think it's for the best.{NOTE:その方がいいと思うんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh…{NOTE:ほ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:22.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Are you serious?{NOTE:本気ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.53,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:38.88,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Captain…{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.09,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.76,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Bear with me. Please be patient.{NOTE:耐えられるんだ。グッと耐えれてくれよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Professor.{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It's time to go to the match. Get ready.{NOTE:さ。試合に行く時間だ。支度たまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.15,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:00.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,– Also, Hayakawa.\N– Sir.{NOTE:—それから、早川。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,For time being, you're the captain.{NOTE:当分は君はキャプテンだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.21,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's cruel. That was too cruel.{NOTE:酷い。酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't take it.{NOTE:あんまり酷すぎるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not from our professor…{NOTE:先生までがあたしをあんなに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:26.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I have no idea what to do next.{NOTE:でも、でもあたし…どうしたらいいか分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:34.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I won't be able to return to volleyball if I lose my captain title like this.{NOTE:あんなふりしてキャプて下ろされたら、もうバレー部には戻れないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:52.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If you take volleyball from me,\Nwhat will remain of me?{NOTE:あたしにバレーがなくなった、何が残るかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:59.20,Alternative,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, watch this.{NOTE:鮎原さん、XXXよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.46,Alternative,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.18,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.93,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,When will we play?{NOTE:何時試合しますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.93,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you.{NOTE:待っていますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No. I won't falter.{NOTE:いいやだ。いいやだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:23.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting.{NOTE:あたしはバレーを止めない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:25.61,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's no way I am.{NOTE:絶対に止めないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am not quitting!{NOTE:絶対に止めないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.20,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I won't quit volleyball no matter what.{NOTE:あたしは絶対にバレーを止めない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:41.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even if I'm all alone, I will continue playing.{NOTE:一人に成っても、断然バレーを続ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll show everyone!{NOTE:続けて見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:56.47,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Ayuhara Kozue challenges the world on the cliff.{NOTE:挑戦と砂浜に佇む鮎原こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:24:00.89,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,She goes to see Fujimi Academy's girls university training.{NOTE:そして、いつしか富士見大学バレー部の練習を見に来ていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:04.94,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Is it possible for Kozue to recover her captain title?{NOTE:キャプテンXXを割れたこずえはもはや立ち直れないのだろうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:10.15,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Captain Oohara holds a hard training session with Kozue.{NOTE:大学バレー部のキャプテン大原はそんなこずえにあまりにも厳しい特訓をかせた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:13.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,They train fiercely on a vacant lof of a factory.{NOTE:ある工場の空き地、救急箱まで用意されている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:17.45,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, Kozue is unable to focus, blaming herself for what happened.{NOTE:だが、こずえは自分を責めるかのように立ち向かっていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:21.54,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタッカーナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
